Online search:

-Search from hundreds of thousands of wines online. 
-Recommendations from critics and consumers.

Flexibility and Freedom:

-Rearrange, rename and create your own wine categories.
-Sort your cellar by vintage or name in ascending or descending order
-Duplicate wines.
-Search wines multiple filters e.g.( Red wines + wines made in France).
-Arrange cellar row information how they are arranged and shown. e.g. location, row number, vintage, etc.

Photos:

-Add infinite number of photos to a single wine at any resolution.
-Pinch and zoom all your photos in full screen mode.

-Auto detects your currency, and allows currency changes.
-Text support for all languages and special characters.

-Dropbox transfer between iPhones and iPads .
